  p
    | Samia's website needed to also work on mobile devices.
    | The cards for each project on her main landing page are arranged in a vertical stack on mobile devices, foregoing the random positioning and animation.
    | Her full portfolio pages for each project also use the same vertical column approach with all pictures, videos, and text stacking on top of one another.
    | The click-and-drag functionality on text write-ups within portfolio pages is also disabled on mobile, allowing users to scroll through the page without a confusing or counter-intuitive&nbsp;experience.

